    bibo:volume "3149" ;
    dc:creator "Cohen, Simone Chinicz; Kohn, Anna; Boeger, Walter A." ;
    dc:date "2012" ;
    dc:title "Neotropical Monogenoidea. 57. Nine new species of Dactylogyridae (Monogenoidea) from the gill of Salminus brasiliensis (Characidae, Characiformes) from the Paraná River, State of Paraná, Brazil" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214568> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.214568>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 10. Sclerotized parts of Anacanthorus spp. from the dourado, Salminus brasiliensis, from Paraná River, Brazil. Figs. 1 – 2. Anacanthorus bicuspidatus 1. Copulatory complex (dorsal view). 2. Hook. Figs. 3 – 4. Anacanthorus contortus sp. n 3. Copulatory complex (dorsal view). 4. Hook. Figs. 5 – 6. Anacanthorus daulometrus sp. n. 5. Copulatory complex (ventral view). 6. Hook. Figs. 7 – 8. Anacanthorus douradensis sp. n.. 7. Copulatory complex (dorsal view). 8. Hook. Figs. 9 – 10. Anacanthorus kruidenieri sp. n. 9. Copulatory complex (dorsal view). 10. Hook. Fig. 7 is presented to the 50 µm scale; Figs. 2, 4, 6, 8 and 10 to the 10 µm scale; Figs. 1, 3, 5 and 9 to the 30 µm scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/214568/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

